<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>人生的智慧 on 布斯行</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/</link><description>Recent content in 人生的智慧 on 布斯行</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 13 Oct 2020 22:45:56 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>吼呆时刻287-人生之老年期</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-13-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB287-%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E8%80%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%9F/</link><pubDate>Tue, 13 Oct 2020 22:45:56 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-13-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB287-%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E8%80%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%9F/</guid><description>无论人们如何为生活着色、打扮，人生从本质上而言，不过就是这样的一种存在：衡量它的真正价值的方法只能是视乎它缺少痛苦的程度，而不是它是否欠缺欢娱，更不是通过生活中的奢华场面。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻286-人生的各个阶段</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-12-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB286-%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E4%B8%AA%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5/</link><pubDate>Mon, 12 Oct 2020 09:07:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-12-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB286-%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E4%B8%AA%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5/</guid><description>我们终其一生都只是生活在现时此刻。不同时期的现时此刻相互之间的差别在于：在生命开始的时候，我们前面是长远的未来；但在生命临近结束时，我们却看到了我们身后走过的漫长的过去。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻285-对命运和事态发展的态度</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB285-%E5%AF%B9%E5%91%BD%E8%BF%90%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%80%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E6%80%81%E5%BA%A6/</link><pubDate>Sun, 11 Oct 2020 23:14:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB285-%E5%AF%B9%E5%91%BD%E8%BF%90%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%80%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E6%80%81%E5%BA%A6/</guid><description>人生的际遇、历险，获得的幸福或者遭受的不幸尽管千差万别，生活仍然就像糖果一样：尽管糖果的形状千奇百怪、颜色多种多样，但都是由同一样的糖果浆做成。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻284-对待他人的态度</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-10-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB284-%E5%AF%B9%E5%BE%85%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%80%81%E5%BA%A6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Oct 2020 23:34:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-10-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB284-%E5%AF%B9%E5%BE%85%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%80%81%E5%BA%A6/</guid><description>尽管两个人所谈论的都是一些陌生和每一个人都不可能看到自身之外的东西</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻283-对待自己的态度</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-09-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB283-%E5%AF%B9%E5%BE%85%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%80%81%E5%BA%A6/</link><pubDate>Fri, 09 Oct 2020 08:41:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-09-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB283-%E5%AF%B9%E5%BE%85%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%80%81%E5%BA%A6/</guid><description>人生智慧的重要一点就是在关注现在和计划将来这两者之间达致恰到好处的平衡，这样，现在与将来才不至于互相干扰。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻282-泛论</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-08-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB282-%E6%B3%9B%E8%AE%BA/</link><pubDate>Thu, 08 Oct 2020 23:22:54 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-08-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB282-%E6%B3%9B%E8%AE%BA/</guid><description>所谓“幸福的生活”，实应被理解为“减少了许多不幸的生活”，亦即还能勉强忍受的生活。确实，生活并不是让我们享受的，我们必须忍受它和克服它。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻281-荣誉</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-07-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB281-%E8%8D%A3%E8%AA%89/</link><pubDate>Wed, 07 Oct 2020 22:07:40 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-07-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB281-%E8%8D%A3%E8%AA%89/</guid><description>不管一个人是谁，他干的职业是什么，只要他破坏了诚和信，他也就永远地失去了诚和信，随之而来的苦果肯定在所难免。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻280-展现的表象</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-06-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB280-%E5%B1%95%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E8%B1%A1/</link><pubDate>Tue, 06 Oct 2020 23:24:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-06-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB280-%E5%B1%95%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E8%B1%A1/</guid><description>骄傲的大敌——就是虚荣</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻279-人所拥有的财富</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-05-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB279-%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%80%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 05 Oct 2020 22:36:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-05-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB279-%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%80%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A2%E5%AF%8C/</guid><description>当对某一样东西的要求还没有进入一个人的意识的时候，这个人完全不会感觉到对它有所欠缺。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻278-人的自身</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-04-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB278-%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB/</link><pubDate>Sun, 04 Oct 2020 22:04:55 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-04-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB278-%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB/</guid><description>对生活稍作考察就可以知道：痛苦和无聊是人类幸福的两个死敌。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻277-人生的智慧</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-03-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB277-%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/</link><pubDate>Sat, 03 Oct 2020 23:51:01 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/2020-10-03-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB277-%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7/</guid><description>同一样外在的事物和同一样的境遇，对于我们每一个人的影响都不尽相同；处在同一样的环境的每一个人，都生活在不同的世界中。</description></item></channel></rss>